# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [0.3.0] - 2024-01-09

### Added

- `bbox_inches` parameter for `AnimatedFigure` to set the saving bounding box.

### Removed

- `fig_kw` parameter for `AnimatedFigure`.

## [0.2.2] - 2024-01-02

### Changed

- Add an erosion step to the diff mask to fix border effects.

## [0.2.0] - 2023-12-14

### Added

- Dependency on `imageio`

### Changed

- Output diffs between successive images in an animation to save space.

## [0.1.1] - 2023-11-13

### Fixed

- Use `display.Markdown` instead of `print`, which was not working anymore.
